name: Formwork concrete cube
description:
These handmade concrete cubes are inspired by modernist architecture and my interest in material integrity and the inbuilt beauty of concrete. These are one off artworks

Dimensions are 8x8x8cm (each)
Cubes can be purchased individually or as multiples
